---
title: Haloumi, Eggplant & Hummus Burger with Harissa Onion & Kumara Wedges
description: Haloumi is one of our favourite burger ingredients - the hearty cheese makes for a filling and flavourful meal. But the flavour doesn't stop there, no we have roasted eggplant, mildly spiced onions and a generous spread of hummus to turn the whole thing into a Middle Eastern burger feast!
